Any communication, internal document, presentation, or material that references, uses, or discusses "The Protocol" must provide prominent and clear attribution to "Wilbert Contreras Borda" as the original architect and author. In permitted publications, this attribution must be in a clearly visible location (e.g., the acknowledgments section of a paper or the credits page of software).

