In the specific case that the application of "The Protocol" leads directly to the complete and recognized solution of a prized mathematical problem (e.g., the Clay Mathematics Institute's Millennium Prize Problems), all monetary awards, primary intellectual recognition, and associated publication rights shall belong entirely to Wilbert Contreras Borda, unless a prior, written collaboration agreement stipulates different terms.

